§6Generators and machines may not be the easiest thing to handle, but once you have your automated systems up and running, they require little to no effort to keep up. Also, if not having to work isn't enough to convince you, you're also able to build unnecessary large storage units.

§7Alright, you want to get work done? You want effective tools? You want to get all the ores on this planet? Then this is the perfect job for you. We utilize whatever other professions developed over time to achieve our only goal: farm as many resources as humanly possible.

§2Plants? What are plants even good for? Well, let me tell you. Not only are they useful for magic, their magic tends to be more environmentally friendly than those of other schools of magic. Additionally, herbalists also have access to certain special crops that are otherwise hard to get.

§b§bTransmutation is the heart of alchemy. Exchanging items for others of equal value allows alchemists to bypass a lot of the tedious crafting of complicated items. Additionally, it's also possible to create high-energy resources and overly powerful tools through alchemy. However, creating them costs thousands of diamonds.
§cMagic, blood, power. This is what you're here for and this is what sorcery will grant you.
